original_title: 業務連絡。頼むぞ、片山部長! in さいたまスーパーアリーナ
overview: AKB48's Spring Concert in 2012, held in Saitama Super Area. The concert was renamed after Maeda Atsuko's graduation announcement.
tagline: Gyomu Renraku. Tanomuzo, Katayama Bucho! in Saitama Super Arena
title: Gyomu Renraku. Tanomuzo, Katayama Bucho! in Saitama Super Arena
